    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-80a0-8933-d48cb0292468",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors introduce a novel way of addressing the group formation challenge using binary integer formulation. 32 students were divided into two sections - one with the suggested method and the second formed teams using a modified version of k-means. Proposed model optimally solved the problem in 8 secs.  ",
